title: Leading A Peasant Mob: Rise of the Partizani - Mount and Blade: Napoleonic Wars Gameplay
description:
Leading a Peasant Mod: Rise of the Partizani - Mount and Blade: Napoleonic Wars Gameplay - Welcome Back to Call to Arms.  Today we are playing a massive line battle!  And to make it challenging for us we are fighting as the Partizani! Lionheartx10 is fighting as the Uk and we are fight as Russia. This one is really fun and challenging since we are at a huge disadvantage.  Enjoy the battle :D

Oasis Hosting Discount Code: https://oasis-hosting.net/gameservers/mbwb/?discountCode=pa2017
